<p class="description">  A thumbnail can be used to show a thumbnail picture/profile picture for an  entity. It will also attempt to set a default thumbnail in case no actual  image is available, and it allows for showing a visibility icon combined with  the thumbnail. These thumbnails will adjust in size to the space they have  been given by their container.    </p>
